MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

This repository packages the original "scroll-svg-design" and
"scroll-interaction" skills from Anthropic's skills repository with:

- A bilingual (English/Chinese) README for improved accessibility
- This NOTICE file for third-party attribution
- Project reorganization for standalone use

The original SKILL.md files and template code remain unmodified.
